# ─── LangChain AI Model Configuration ─────────────────────────────────────
# ScholarAId uses LangChain for AI with multiple free model providers.
# The system auto-selects the best available model based on API keys.
#
# Priority: Google Gemini > Groq > z-ai-web-dev-sdk (fallback)
#
# Option 1: Google Gemini (FREE - Best quality)
#   Get your free API key at: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
#   Free tier: 15 RPM, 1M tokens/min, 1500 RPD
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_google_api_key_here
#
# Option 2: Groq (FREE - Fastest response)
#   Get your free API key at: https://console.groq.com/keys
#   Free tier: 30 RPM, 14400 requests/day
# GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here
#
# If no keys are set, the system uses the built-in z-ai-web-dev-sdk (always available).
